Media Query Breaks

Typical Breakpoints (Mobile-First min-width):
Breakpoint	Pixels	Devices
min-width: 480px	480px	Small phones (landscape)
min-width: 576px	576px	Larger phones, small devices
min-width: 768px	768px	Tablets (e.g., iPad portrait)
min-width: 992px	992px	Tablets (landscape), small laptops
min-width: 1200px	1200px	Desktops, larger laptops
min-width: 1400px	1400px	Very large screens


@media (min-width: 768px) {
    example {
        flex-direction: row;
    }
}